programme.title: Live PRO14 Rugby Union
programme.desc: Leinster v Ulster (Kick-off 5.35pm). Coverage of the match from the 13th round of fixtures, as the Irish rivals face each other at Royal Dublin Society. When the teams met in the reverse fixture at Kingspan Stadium last October, Ulster suffered a first home defeat in the PRO14 in a year as Leinster claimed a 25-10 victory, which was also the visitors' first win in Belfast since 2014. With both teams faring well in Conference B this term, they will be keen to register a victory over a fellow contender for a place in the end-of-season play-offs
